freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: 10 days after vaccine, injection site got irritated & itchy & I had a quarter size & a dime-size lump come up. I massaged area & tried not to scratch. Lumps remained about 24 hours, itchiness is intermittent.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Coughing, strange feeling in chest, difficulty breathing
Diarrhea yesterday after I completed check in
Size of injection site redness continues to increase.
